    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Raincoats of rubberized cloth; use especially for those made with India rubber following a technique invented by Charles Mackintosh (1766-1843).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
